title: RHOSLC TRAILER! + RHOBH in Aspen!

Danny recaps the season 3 trailer for The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City and boy are we in for a ride!!!! Then Danny recaps The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which saw the cast go to Aspen, conjure some spirits, and not grill any corn.
